"recipe.it_lasagna_alla_bolognese.drink.body" = "Pair with Sangiovese or a dry Lambrusco to cut through the richness and match the ragù. A fuller-bodied white with good acidity can also work. Non-alcoholic option: sparkling water or a lightly bitter citrus soda.";
