"recipe.it_lasagna_alla_bolognese.info" = "A traditional Emilia-Romagna lasagna made with fresh egg pasta sheets layered with slow-cooked ragù and béchamel, finished with Parmigiano-Reggiano. Baked until bubbling and lightly browned, it is served in generous slices for family Sundays and celebrations, prized for its rich, cohesive layers and deep savory flavor.";
