"recipe.it_spaghetti_alla_carbonara.drink.summary" = "Frascati or red";
"recipe.it_spaghetti_alla_carbonara.info" = "A traditional Roman pasta where hot spaghetti is coated in a silky emulsion of egg, Pecorino Romano, and rendered guanciale fat, finished with plenty of black pepper. Served immediately while glossy and hot, carbonara is a staple of trattorias and home kitchens, valued for its richness and careful technique.";
