"recipe.it_tagliatelle_ragu_bolognese.step3.body" = "Add olive oil and butter, then add the chopped onion, carrot, and celery. Cook slowly, stirring, until soft and fragrant without browning.";
"recipe.it_tagliatelle_ragu_bolognese.step3.title" = "Soften the vegetables";
"recipe.it_tagliatelle_ragu_bolognese.step4.body" = "Add ground beef and ground pork. Break up the meat and cook until it loses its raw color and starts to brown lightly.";
"recipe.it_tagliatelle_ragu_bolognese.step4.title" = "Brown the meat";
"recipe.it_tagliatelle_ragu_bolognese.step5.body" = "Pour in the wine and let it simmer until the sharp alcohol smell fades and most of the liquid has reduced.";
